The `dictionary` list is not null.
The `sentence` string is not null.
The `dictionary` list contains only lowercase letters.
The length of each word in the `dictionary` list is between 1 and 100.
The `sentence` string contains only lowercase letters and spaces.
The length of each word in the `sentence` string is between 1 and 100.
Every two consecutive words in the `sentence` string are separated by exactly one space.
The `sentence` string does not have leading or trailing spaces.
